]

#block(inset: 8pt, radius: 4pt, stroke: 0.4pt)[#emph[The Polite Interest Trap]
#v(3pt)
People saying 'cool idea' is not demand. Demand looks like questions, urgency, payment, referrals, or asking when it’s available.

#emph[Notes]
#v(3pt)
